00:21:59.420 --> 00:22:06.970 line:20%
Plan B

00:21:59.790 --> 00:22:02.590
It's the first day of school
and she lost a point.

00:22:02.590 --> 00:22:05.570
To top it off, her relationship with
Damian couldn't be any worse.

00:22:07.550 --> 00:22:10.050
All right, everyone! We're taking the picture!

00:22:10.050 --> 00:22:13.710
The family on the right over there!
Smile a little more!

00:22:13.710 --> 00:22:15.550
Say, "Cheese!"

